eyyāti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv13.1:3.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.3":{"pli":"Kappaṭṭho kappe ḍayhante kattha gacchatīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.4":{"pli":"Aññaṁ lokadhātuṁ gacchatīti. ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.5":{"pli":"Mato gacchati, vehāsaṁ gacchatīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.6":{"pli":"Mato gacchatīti. ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.7":{"pli":"Kappaṭṭhiyaṁ kammaṁ aparāpariyavepakkanti? ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.8":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.9":{"pli":"vehāsaṁ gacchatīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.10":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.11":{"pli":"Kappaṭṭho iddhimāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.12":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.13":{"pli":"kappaṭṭho iddhimāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.14":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.15":{"pli":"Kappaṭṭhena chandiddhipādo bhāvito vīriyiddhipādo bhāvito cittiddhipādo bhāvito vīmaṁsiddhipādo bhāvitoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:3.16":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe…. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv13.1:4.1":{"pli":"Na vattabbaṁ—","html":"<p data-doxy='heterodox'>{}"},"kv13.1:4.2":{"pli":"“kappaṭṭho kappaṁ tiṭṭheyyā”ti? ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:4.3":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:4.4":{"pli":"Nanu vuttaṁ bhagavatā—","html":"{}</p>"},"kv13.1:5.1":{"pli":"“Āpāyiko nerayiko, ","html":"<blockquote class='gatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv13.1:5.2":{"pli":"Kappaṭṭho saṅghabhedako; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv13.1:5.3":{"pli":"Vaggarato adhammaṭṭho, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv13.1:5.4":{"pli":"Yogakkhemā padhaṁsati; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv13.1:5.5":{"pli":"Saṅghaṁ samaggaṁ bhetvāna, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv13.1:5.6":{"pli":"Kappaṁ nirayamhi paccatī”ti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"kv13.1:6.1":{"pli":"Attheva suttantoti? ","html":"<p>{}"},"kv13.1:6.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv13.1:6.3":{"pli":